{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja template for Spectra LS Phase 3 S01/S02 closure gate decision. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.19.1 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-19 #}

{# =========================
  Phase 3 S01/S02 Closure Gate Check (custom_components/spectra_ls)
  Purpose: single deterministic closeout verdict for P3-S01/S02.

  Operator inputs (edit these 4 values before running):
    - observed_soak_pass_cycles
    - observed_soak_attempts
    - observed_distinct_pass_targets
    - single_capable_topology_waiver

  Notes:
  - This template does NOT replace S01/S02 templates; it consumes their expected outcomes + soak evidence.
  - Use after running one-shot and soak protocol evidence capture.
  ========================= #}

{% set observed_soak_pass_cycles = 3 %}
{% set observed_soak_attempts = 5 %}
{% set observed_distinct_pass_targets = 1 %}
{% set single_capable_topology_waiver = true %}

{% set s_target = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' if states['sensor.shadow_active_target'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_path = 'sensor.shadow_active_control_path' if states['sensor.shadow_active_control_path'] is not none else 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_control_path' %}

{% set active_target = states(s_target) %}
{% set active_path = states(s_path) %}

{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target,'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set route_reason = route_trace.reason if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.reason is defined else '' %}

{% set contract_validation = state_attr(s_target,'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set contract_ready = contract_validation is mapping and contract_validation.valid is defined %}
{% set contract_valid = contract_validation.valid if contract_ready else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract_validation.missing_required if contract_ready and contract_validation.missing_required is defined else [] %}

{% set parity_unresolved = state_attr(s_target,'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set parity_mismatches = state_attr(s_target,'mismatches') or [] %}

{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target,'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else '' %}
{% set last_attempt = write_controls.last_attempt if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.last_attempt is defined and write_controls.last_attempt is mapping else {} %}
{% set last_status = last_attempt.status if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.status is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set last_reason = last_attempt.reason if last_attempt is mapping and last_attempt.reason is defined else '' %}

{% set handoff = state_attr(s_target,'selection_handoff_validation') or {} %}
{% set handoff_verdict = handoff.verdict if handoff is mapping and handoff.verdict is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set handoff_ready = handoff.ready_for_handoff if handoff is mapping and handoff.ready_for_handoff is defined else false %}
{% set compat = handoff.compatibility if handoff is mapping and handoff.compatibility is defined and handoff.compatibility is mapping else {} %}
{% set missing_scripts = compat.missing_scripts if compat is mapping and compat.missing_scripts is defined else [] %}
{% set missing_automation_ids = compat.missing_automation_ids if compat is mapping and compat.missing_automation_ids is defined else [] %}

{% set pass_status_component = ['write_applied', 'noop_already_selected', 'blocked_debounce', 'blocked_reentrancy'] %}

{% set gate_route_ok = route_decision == 'route_linkplay_tcp' %}
{% set gate_contract_ok = contract_ready and contract_valid and (missing_required | length) == 0 %}
{% set gate_parity_ok = (parity_unresolved | length) == 0 and (parity_mismatches | length) == 0 %}
{% set gate_s01_ok = authority_mode == 'component' and last_status in pass_status_component %}
{% set gate_s02_ok = handoff_verdict == 'PASS' and handoff_ready and (missing_scripts | length) == 0 and (missing_automation_ids | length) == 0 %}
{% set gate_soak_cycles_ok = observed_soak_pass_cycles >= 3 %}
{% set gate_distinct_targets_ok = observed_distinct_pass_targets >= 2 or single_capable_topology_waiver %}

{% set gate_ok_count = 0 %}
{% if gate_route_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if gate_contract_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if gate_parity_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if gate_s01_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if gate_s02_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if gate_soak_cycles_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}
{% if gate_distinct_targets_ok %}{% set gate_ok_count = gate_ok_count + 1 %}{% endif %}

{% set verdict = 'PASS' %}
{% if gate_ok_count < 5 %}
  {% set verdict = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif gate_ok_count < 7 %}
  {% set verdict = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

### Phase 3 S01/S02 Closure Gate Check (`spectra_ls`)
- Result: **{{ verdict }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**
- Gate score: **{{ gate_ok_count }}/7**

### Runtime context
- Active target (`{{ s_target }}`): **{{ active_target }}**
- Active path (`{{ s_path }}`): **{{ active_path }}**
- Route decision/reason: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}** / **{{ route_reason if route_reason != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Authority mode: **{{ authority_mode if authority_mode != '' else 'n/a' }}**
- Last write attempt: **{{ last_status }}** (reason={{ last_reason if last_reason != '' else 'n/a' }})
- Handoff verdict/ready: **{{ handoff_verdict }} / {{ handoff_ready }}**

### Soak evidence inputs (operator-supplied)
- Observed soak pass cycles: **{{ observed_soak_pass_cycles }}**
- Observed soak attempts: **{{ observed_soak_attempts }}**
- Observed distinct PASS targets: **{{ observed_distinct_pass_targets }}**
- Single-capable-topology waiver enabled: **{{ single_capable_topology_waiver }}**

### Gate breakdown
- Route is eligible (`route_linkplay_tcp`): **{{ gate_route_ok }}**
- Contract valid + no missing required: **{{ gate_contract_ok }}**
- Parity clean (`unresolved=0`, `mismatches=0`): **{{ gate_parity_ok }}**
- S01 guarded-write status healthy: **{{ gate_s01_ok }}**
- S02 handoff compatibility healthy: **{{ gate_s02_ok }}**
- Soak cycles sufficient (>=3): **{{ gate_soak_cycles_ok }}**
- Distinct target gate (>=2 or waiver): **{{ gate_distinct_targets_ok }}**

### Compatibility details
- Missing required contract entities: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- Missing scripts: **{{ missing_scripts | length }}**
- Missing automation IDs: **{{ missing_automation_ids | length }}**
- Parity unresolved/mismatches: **{{ parity_unresolved | length }} / {{ parity_mismatches | length }}**

### Closure recommendation
{% if verdict == 'PASS' %}
- **Recommend close P3-S01:** Yes
- **Recommend close P3-S02:** Yes
- Record closure note in roadmap + v-next + changelog with the soak/waiver evidence above.
{% elif verdict == 'WARN' %}
- **Recommend close P3-S01:** {{ 'Yes' if gate_s01_ok and gate_route_ok and gate_contract_ok and gate_parity_ok else 'No' }}
- **Recommend close P3-S02:** No
- Remaining blockers are listed in the gate breakdown; resolve and rerun.
{% else %}
- **Recommend close P3-S01:** No
- **Recommend close P3-S02:** No
- Resolve FAIL gates first; do not advance to P3-S03/Phase 4.
{% endif %}
